---
layout: base.njk
title: Submit Information
permalink: /submit/index.html
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Community submissions</p>
  <h1>Send a tip or article</h1>
  <p>Share a correction, document, source link, article idea, or timeline entry.</p>
</section>

<section class="section split">
  <div>
    <h2>Help build the record</h2>
    <p>Include clear dates, source links, names, and any context needed to understand the information.</p>
    <p class="fine-print">The form sends submissions through Netlify Forms. Find messages in the Netlify project under Forms.</p>
  </div>

  <form class="submission-form" name="truthoutlaw-submissions" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
    <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="truthoutlaw-submissions">
    <p class="hidden">
      <label>Leave this empty: <input name="bot-field"></label>
    </p>
    <label>
      Name
      <input name="name" type="text" placeholder="Optional">
    </label>
    <label>
      Email
      <input name="email" type="email" placeholder="Optional">
    </label>
    <label>
      Subject
      <input name="subject" type="text" required placeholder="What is this about?">
    </label>
    <label>
      Information
      <textarea name="message" rows="9" required placeholder="Include dates, links, sources, and relevant details."></textarea>
    </label>
    <button class="button primary" type="submit">Send submission</button>
  </form>
</section>
